headline: In response to customer demand, Textron Aviation adds Starlink high-speed internet availability to Cessna Citation Sovereign and Sovereign+
summary: WICHITA, Kan., July 10, 2025--Textron Aviation announced an additional high-speed internet connectivity solution for the Cessna Citation Sovereign and Sovereign+.
